description:
We talk to Tim Tebow about his new motivational book, where he seems himself in 10 to 15 year and even a little college football talk! Amy reveals she got paid way too much on her last checks and asks us what she should do next? The return of “pick a bit” where the show gets to decide what segment we talk about next…
